Package com.loginscreen

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IPresenter
    Interface that acts as a presenter between view classes and model classes.
    IView
    Interface that acts as a view for presenter classes and model classes.
    IVolleyListener
    Interface that uses the Volley library and is implemented within presenter classes.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ChangePassword
    Class to be removed!
    ExampleInstrumentedTest
    Instrumented test, which will execute on an Android device.
    ExampleUnitTest
    Example local unit test, which will execute on the development machine (host).
    ForgotPassword
    Currently, the class is not finished nor does it work.
    LoginActivity
    View class of the login action of the user.
    LoginActivityModel
    Class calls a GET request that will return a response containing a JSONArray of users.
    LoginActivityPresenter
    Class acts as the presenter between the LoginActivityModel and LoginActivity view class.
    UserRegisterActivity
    View class of the registration of the user to join the Infinity application.
    UserRegisterModel
    Class calls a GET request that will return a response containing a JSONArray of users, and it also calls a POST request to enter the user's input credentials into the database.
    UserRegisterPresenter
    Class acts as the presenter between the UserRegisterModel and UserRegisterActivity view class.
